      "name": "Shadow Acid",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The tenebrous worm spews a @Template[type:cone|distance:30] of shadowy acid dealing [[/r {10d6}[acid]]]{10d6 acid damage} to every creature within the cone (@Check[type:reflex|dc:28]) if this ability was used in dim light. If Shadow Acid is used in bright light or darkness, the damage is reduced to [[/r {5d6}[acid]]]{5d6 acid damage}. The tenebrous worm can't use Shadow Acid again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
